Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起 我就是爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個健康的男孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准碰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要先見媽媽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於相見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖哦 乖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛名 感覺好些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 雖然剛生完孩子很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要抓緊將九尾完全抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琵琶子大人 多慈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四代火影 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我離開人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然這孩子的壽命就只有一分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎麼穿過結界的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾的封印還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊離開人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管這小鬼的死活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話還是對你自己說吧 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是相當冷靜的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是黃色閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可接下來如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 鳴人沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫使出了飛雷神之術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目標是櫛名…調虎離山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得抓緊時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想…做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你體內奪走九尾以摧毀木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人的瞬身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能瞬間穿梭於設下術式標記的各個空間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你的封印式上也有那個標記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人時刻都在保護著你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在總算被支開來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且九尾的封印因為分娩正不斷減弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這千載難逢的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我等了多久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 稍微等我一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在必須趕緊去救你媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 出來吧 九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就這樣直接前往木葉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦一族真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾獸被剝離了也不會立刻死亡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是九尾人柱力的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓九尾葬送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪被稱為閃光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…鳴人沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 馬上去阻止那個男人和九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要去木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我們這就去木葉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 你留在鳴人身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人…謝謝你…一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有一顆流星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次有沒有許願呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出去想幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是男人間的應酬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼難得啊 最近每晚都是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡量速戰速決啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下次會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我好好走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有更激烈一點的較量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣還算是我的對手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明早還得早起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少用任務來做擋箭牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這滿腔的熱血多得無處發洩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是鍛煉的大好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是這點滴努力的積累
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是未來任務成功的關鍵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這個了 凱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得有些不對勁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才起 就覺得空氣很冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的是你的態度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春可是稍縱即逝的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個感覺是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不詳的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼偏偏這個時候 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽都不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼事 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥都會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代火影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾…九尾出現在村裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們前去保護非戰鬥人員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛名的封印被解開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經那樣嚴防死守了 還是失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琵琶子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡啊 九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻正是釋放我這火熱能量的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太過輕率 凱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來 我才是你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這就前往避難處集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是前代大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日斬大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧 走了 凱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 非戰鬥人員趕緊避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這邊 九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊呢 九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使無法打倒九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保證居民順利避難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絕不能讓九尾前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快前往日斬大人那兒集合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴格執行命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上火影之名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護村子裡的家人們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我現在應盡的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許你繼續肆意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你為所欲為的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力如此之大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈飛的落點也要謹慎選擇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移九尾攻擊的那個術…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時空間結界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是皆人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我們也上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須立刻向第三代匯報此事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍遷了嗎 真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我要比你更快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接觸的一瞬間…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的攻擊直接穿過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之後立刻實體化想將我吸入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什麼術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也能使用時空間忍術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帶著櫛名立刻轉移也是因為這個能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破第三代直屬暗部的防線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入最高機密下的結界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道九尾的封印會在分娩時減弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能解開九尾的封印 並將其馴服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且不受木葉結界的阻撓 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由出入的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知 僅有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是宇智波斑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下你是誰無關緊要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵是你為何要襲擊木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是一時興起吧 也可以說是蓄謀已久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既是為了戰爭 也是為了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 他都絕非等閒之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有控制九尾的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有超越第二代跟我的時空間忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上極端危險的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不就此做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後他會比九尾更麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我轉移回村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也會跟去 戰場則會更加混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他是斑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也無法長時間召喚九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡只有仰仗第三代了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須在這裡解決他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今九尾已經被我解放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經毫無希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物理攻擊對他的肉身無效
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他在攻擊時必須實體化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說只能抓住對攻的瞬間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對他而言 攻擊會帶來危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上召喚九尾的時間限制
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該也想速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負關鍵就在於誰的攻擊更快了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他轉移到剛才的苦無上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是飛雷神的第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擺了一道 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的神出鬼沒就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能有半點大意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛雷神之術…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:21:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 他在我身體的某處留下了標記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要從我這分離九尾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 九尾就不再屬於你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依魯卡 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.22,0:22:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不老實待在避難所裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能留下爸爸媽媽獨自逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼不要逞能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護孩子是父母的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免村子被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把九尾從趕到村外去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的術完成之前 替我爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊絕不能懈怠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法.通靈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:23:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧 猿猴王 猿魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾啊 封印被解開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將它趕出村子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用金剛如意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 變化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了 猿魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經趕出村外了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要鬆懈 持續攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是第四代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能傷到我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並將九尾與我分離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:23:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過九尾終究還是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我注定是這個世界的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦法多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.35,0:24:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種感覺…並不是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.24,0:24:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第四代趕來前先壓制住它
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.47,0:24:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依魯卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.12,0:24:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽還在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.19,0:24:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.18,0:24:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們年輕的一代不可以接近九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.80,0:24:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.44,0:24:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並非是村子間的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.94,0:24:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是村子內部的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.05,0:24:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你們捨命而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.11,0:24:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.77,0:25:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 紅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.16,0:25:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為忍者 生死由不得自己
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.32,0:25:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的女兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.20,0:25:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你至少要將火之意志托付給我的孫兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.71,0:25:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把它當作同父親的約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.75,0:25:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.36,0:25:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.02,0:25:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想用那招嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.03,0:25:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.78,0:25:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.96,0:25:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.65,0:25:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第四代
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.58,0:25:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我注定是這個世界的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.70,0:25:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛名 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.74,0:25:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時替我壓制住九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.82,0:26:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我 也有點力不從心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.43,0:26:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要轉移這麼大的東西需要相應的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.92,0:26:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.88,0:26:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連九尾一起躍遷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.69,0:26:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.83,0:26:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須馬上張開結界…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.89,0:26:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.77,0:26:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能行…皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.38,0:26:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛名
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.10,0:26:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.24,0:26:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.21,0:27:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛名
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.62,0:27:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就這樣…將九尾拖入體內同歸於盡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.84,0:27:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就能延長九尾下次復活的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.25,0:27:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑我僅有的查克拉想幫你也只能如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.79,0:27:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來多謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.80,0:27:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛名 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.46,0:27:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓我成為了第四代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.30,0:27:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我成為了你的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.63,0:27:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓我成為了這孩子的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.35,0:27:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.34,0:27:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 別露出這種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.23,0:27:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.53,0:27:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一直被你愛著…而且
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.81,0:27:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還是孩子的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.38,0:28:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.32,0:28:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想一家三口溫馨生活的畫面…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.26,0:28:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定非常的幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.30,0:28:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要說還有什麼遺憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.99,0:28:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我好想…看看長大後的鳴人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.87,0:28:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛名 你沒必要和九尾同歸於盡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.36,0:28:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用剩下的查克拉 
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.64,0:28:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鳴人在未來重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.72,0:28:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會將你剩下的查卡拉組合在八卦封印中全部封入鳴人體內
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.05,0:28:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後九尾就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.45,0:28:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非人柱力的我能施展的封印術…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.38,0:28:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有屍鬼封盡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.00,0:29:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個術會將施術者…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.72,0:29:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.81,0:29:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能將九尾封印一半
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.59,0:29:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股巨大的力量理論上無法完全封印
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.89,0:29:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰略上也不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.67,0:29:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你搭上性命封印九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.78,0:29:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那九尾在復活前會因為沒有人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.57,0:29:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而導致尾獸的平衡被打破 那就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.01,0:29:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍鬼封盡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.68,0:29:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠將我和九尾的一半永久封印
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.42,0:29:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而九尾的另一半…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.96,0:29:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許 你就是預言之子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.79,0:29:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.96,0:29:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久的將來 忍者世界將會發生大事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.30,0:29:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的救世主就是預言之子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.40,0:29:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…封印在鳴人體內
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.26,0:29:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用八卦封印
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.84,0:29:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.29,0:29:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自來也老師說過 世界將發生變革
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.72,0:30:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有隨之而來的巨大災難
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.64,0:30:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 我確定了兩件事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.06,0:30:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一是襲擊你的那個面具男
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.44,0:30:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會招來災禍
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.57,0:30:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而能制止這些的…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.96,0:30:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.03,0:30:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也老師命名的這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.11,0:30:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將作為人柱力 替我們開拓未來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.80,0:30:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何我深信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.29,0:30:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.03,0:30:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍鬼封盡
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.27,0:30:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就相信這個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.24,0:30:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是我們的兒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.96,0:30:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個印…難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.63,0:31:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是屍鬼封盡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.13,0:31:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在屍鬼封盡後
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.23,0:31:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把你的查克拉封印到鳴人體內
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.80,0:31:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他作為人柱力想控制九尾時
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.57,0:31:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能助他一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.59,0:31:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們的兒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.33,0:31:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 我才不想讓鳴人背負如此沉重的包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.77,0:31:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且為什麼要用屍鬼封盡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.67,0:31:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了讓我能看看長大後的鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.21,0:31:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就為了那麼短暫的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.77,0:31:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒理由讓你為此賠上性命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.85,0:31:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能留在鳴人身邊見證他的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.50,0:31:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.02,0:31:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因為尾獸的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.25,0:31:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為國家 因為村子而犧牲鳴人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.14,0:32:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要為了我犧牲你自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.55,0:32:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄國家 放棄村子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.09,0:32:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同拋棄自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.00,0:32:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經歷過國破家亡的你應該明白才是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.33,0:32:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有國家的人會承受如何殘酷的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.66,0:32:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們一家…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.28,0:32:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.39,0:32:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 就算我活著也無法代替你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.84,0:32:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是片刻地相見
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.31,0:32:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為母親的你能傳達給鳴人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.51,0:32:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也遠比我多
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.06,0:32:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是母親的責任哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.06,0:32:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不僅是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.58,0:32:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.80,0:32:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為兒子而死又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.41,0:33:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是父親應盡的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.28,0:33:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代 怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.85,0:33:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.11,0:33:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往前就是防止九尾逃出的結界
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.19,0:33:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.27,0:33:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算憑一己之力解決九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.10,0:33:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 第四代火影
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.49,0:33:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.81,0:33:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體都麻痺了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.14,0:33:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這股查克拉會如此沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.34,0:33:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.49,0:33:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是屍鬼封盡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.15,0:33:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真用了這招
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.12,0:34:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是九尾仍舊…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.88,0:34:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法完全封印嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.87,0:34:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然變小了…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.46,0:34:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 接下來就是八卦封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.39,0:34:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將九尾封印到鳴人體內
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.17,0:34:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印儀式用的台座
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.21,0:34:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想再度封印我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.96,0:34:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是那種小鬼的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.24,0:34:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛名 還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.66,0:34:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.63,0:35:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了 這是父親應盡的職責嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.21,0:35:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那母親就更該如此了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.11,0:35:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子也在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.97,0:35:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護住了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.53,0:35:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.49,0:35:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫妻吵架 我還是第一次輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.44,0:35:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 看來你是認真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.96,0:35:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 櫛名
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.26,0:35:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.55,0:35:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.69,0:35:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四代 你這是搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.34,0:35:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛤蟆寅 我將封印式的鑰匙給你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.00,0:35:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立刻去交給自來也老師保管
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.35,0:35:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來皆人想將自己的兒子作為新的人柱力以拯救村子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.40,0:36:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.82,0:36:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.33,0:36:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.38,0:36:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫛名 我快挺不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.16,0:36:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該進行八卦封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.66,0:36:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想將我的查克拉留一點給鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.31,0:36:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要暫時分別了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.17,0:36:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼話想對鳴人說就趁現在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.63,0:36:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 不要挑食…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.14,0:36:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好吃飯 長得壯壯的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.58,0:36:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都要洗澡 別凍著自己
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.21,0:36:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外不要熬夜 得好好睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.78,0:36:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 要交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.32,0:36:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友不需多
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.72,0:37:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾個能真正信賴的朋友就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.04,0:37:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽雖然學得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.73,0:37:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要好好讀書 學習忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.35,0:37:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 誰都有擅長和不擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.66,0:37:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果學不好 也不要氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.63,0:37:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校 要尊重老師和前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.75,0:37:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有件相當重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.29,0:37:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者有三禁
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.84,0:37:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是錢的進出
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.82,0:37:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務報酬要存好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.38,0:37:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有酒 二十歲之後才能喝
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.30,0:37:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要適可而止 酒喝多了會傷身體
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.85,0:37:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而三禁之首就是女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.00,0:37:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽是女人 所以不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.82,0:37:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 這個世界只有女人和男人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.13,0:38:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早晚會喜歡上女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.70,0:38:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但千萬別被壞女人騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.05,0:38:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個像媽媽一樣的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.13,0:38:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到三禁還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.26,0:38:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多加小心自來也老師了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.50,0:38:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.92,0:38:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後會有許多痛苦和磨難
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.41,0:38:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把持住自己 堅持夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.99,0:38:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要有能實現夢想的自信…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.51,0:38:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…還有…還有…還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.93,0:38:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的還有很多事情想一併教給你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.98,0:38:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想能一直陪在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.14,0:38:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.79,0:38:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 對不起 儘是我在說…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.81,0:38:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.18,0:39:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.36,0:39:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸想說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.89,0:39:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個囉嗦的媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.89,0:39:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八卦封印
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.13,0:39:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 讓你成為了九尾的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.66,0:39:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你肩負起我們的重擔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.33,0:39:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有伴你長大
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.93,0:39:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有給你愛的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.18,0:39:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.84,0:39:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是人柱力 以前確實經歷過痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.33,0:39:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我從未憎恨過爸爸和媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.57,0:39:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說 我不太清楚父母的愛是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.00,0:40:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓爸爸和媽媽一直不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.66,0:40:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能模糊地感覺一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.79,0:40:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.99,0:40:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽為我獻出了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.46,0:40:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白早在裝入九尾之前 我這個容器就已經被愛填滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.24,0:40:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.45,0:40:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為爸爸和媽媽的孩子真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.22,0:40:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 你聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.98,0:40:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的愛已經傳達給孩子了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.60,0:40:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.19,0:40:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你讓我成為了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.09,0:40:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你讓皆人成為了爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.77,0:40:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降生為我們的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.68,0:40:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.68,0:40:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.28,0:42:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,鳴人是在這裡戰勝了真實的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.72,0:42:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,凱也想試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.53,0:42:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,少開玩笑了 不說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.65,0:42:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,我可是前來替鳴人助威的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.60,0:42:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,其實你是害怕真實的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.69,0:42:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,什麼 我這就做給你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.87,0:42:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,我總覺得不該讓他去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.00,0:42:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.91,0:42:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,珍獸 VS 怪人 樂園的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.00,0:42:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0002,,這就是真實的我嗎
